    "When I count my blessings,\nI count you twice, maybe thrice.\nYou've made my world so beautiful,\nMy heart's own paradise. ğŸ’–",
    
    "You're the coffee to my morning,\nThe stars to my night sky.\nWith you, every ordinary moment\nBecomes a reason to fly high. â˜•âœ¨",
    
    "Time stands still when you're near,\nThe world fades away but you.\nIn your arms I find my home,\nIn your heart, my dreams come true. ğŸ ğŸ’•",
    
    "You paint colors in my gray days,\nBring music to my silent nights.\nWith every kiss, every touch,\nYou make everything feel right. ğŸ¨ğŸµ",
    
    "Distance means nothing when love means everything,\nMiles apart but hearts as one.\nEvery sunset brings me closer\nTo the day our love has won. ğŸŒ…â¤ï¸",
    
